data.description: GREAT OPPORTUNITY TO MAKE THIS HOUSE YOUR HOME!!  PRICED BELOW MARKET!  Charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath with a vaulted ceiling and cozy fireplace in living area where you can make many memories.  Stainless and black appliances in kitchen and refrigerator stays. Huge primary bedroom with enough room for king sized furniture and a sitting area.  Nice yard with covered patio and open deck along with a full 2 car garage in the rear with opener.  Separate utility room.  Wonderful quiet location in a neighborhood with mature trees.  Walking distance from Mesquite ISD Price Elementary School and close to other schools, Town East Mall and with easy access to 635.
